column31: The Food and Drug Administration (FDA), the agency which has been in the focal point of the long wait for a vaccine, is now in the limelight for a different reason after House leaders filed a resolution calling for a congressional probe on its alleged acceptance of foreign funding in possible violation of the 1987 Constitution and several laws. https://tribune.net.ph/index.php/2020/12/07/house-wants-fda-probed-over-foreign-funding/
column35: House wants FDA probed over foreign funding | Business | Daily Tribune
column36: FDA officials admitted that they received funding from The Union and Bloomberg Initiative which are international private groups that advocate against all forms of tobacco products
